metatags.og:title: 176,200 Ortho Alaska Patients Affected by Data Breach
metatags.og:description: OrthoAlaska has recently notified the HHS' Office for Civil Rights (OCR) about a HIPAA data breach that has affected 176,203 patients. At present, little OrthoAlaska has reported a data breach that has affected more than 176,200 patients. Data breaches have also been reported by Physio Logic Chiropractic and Physical Therapy, Physio Logic Medicine, Dr. Patty DiBlasio, Bluegrass Care Navigators, and Mosaic Mental Health.
